oai_dc:dc.dc:title: The Evolution of a food-animal veterinarian
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Blood, K. Shawn
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The presentation describes the complex internal and external effects that led to my career evolving from associate veterinarian to practice owner to staff veterinarian for a large family owned agriculture enterprise, to a technical services veterinarian for a large animal pharmaceutical and services company.
